author: cmlenz
msg: Experimental implementation of a qualified name cache.
The rational is that a WebDAV server needs to process a lot of
PROPFIND requests, and most of the time the property names are
the same (i.e. the standard DAV: properties). The qualified names are
now kept in a table separate from the SLIDE_REVISION_PROPERTY
table, and similar to URIs, cached in two lookup Hashtables.
I only tested this briefly, and there is no cleanup of unused qualified
